- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with automatic speech recognition and language modeling.

- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper proposes a method to enhance language model probabilities using machine learning techniques.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with improving the performance of automatic speech recognition systems using AI techniques.
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with improving the estimation of low-frequency words, which is a common problem in information retrieval systems.
